<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6533436>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Molecular phylogenies of Eucosmocydia based on COI barcode sequences for 10 species of Eucosmocydia and the outgroups Grapholita chytranthusi, Namasia monitrix, Neonamasia cryptica, Thaumatovalva limbata, Thaumatovalva spinai, and Thaumatotibia leucotreta. BOLD process numbers are given next to species names. a) Maximum likelihood tree; node labels represent boot-strap support values. b) Bayesian consensus tree as derived using MrBayes; node labels represent posterior probabilities." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6533436/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

